N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 13.5 - Dating qualifying certificates

State Regulations
A candidate who submits satisfactory evidence that he has
completed a course of study entitling him to a qualifying certificate may be
granted a qualifying certificate as of the date when he actually completed the
requirements. Notes
